value: 6062 - Credit Unions, Not Federally Chartered Summary > Summerland Financial Services Limited (formerly Summerland Credit Union Limited) provides retail financial services to members. The company was established as a finance provider back in 1964. As a credit union, the business is run to profit members, which are typically from the Northern Rivers region of New South Wales. Summerland Credit Union is based in Lismore, New South Wales. Key Personnel > No key personnel were found for the selected company.
